<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>Saraiva.com.br</title>
	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, minimum-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
</head>
<body class="page-report">
<div class="content-error">
	<img src="data:image/png;base64," class="icon" />
	<h2>Nossos servidores estão em manutenção</h2>
</div>
<style>
* {
	margin:0;
	padding:0;
	box-sizing: border-box;
	-webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
	-moz-box-sizing: border-box;
}

html, body.page-report { height:100%; }

body.page-report {
	padding-top:100px;
	background:#fff url('data:image/jpeg;base64,') repeat-x;
	font:14px 'OpenSans-Regular', Arial, sans-serif;
	color:#000;
}

a {
	color:#444;
	text-decoration:underline;
}
a:hover {
	color:#444;
	text-decoration:none;
}
:focus {
	outline:0;
}
a img {
	border:0;
}
ul,ol {
	list-style:none;
}

.content-error {
	width: 100%;
	max-width: 710px;
	margin: 0 auto;
}
.content-error::after {
	content: '';
	clear: both;
	display: block;
}
.content-error .icon {
	float: left;
	margin-right: 30px;
}
.content-error h2 {
	padding: 40px 0 0 0;
	font:bold 26px 'OpenSans-Bold', Arial, sans-serif;
}

.numer-error {
	position: fixed;
	right: 0;
	bottom: 0;
	padding:2px;
	font-size: 12px;
	color: #fff;
}
</style>
</body>
</html>
